These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, woodworking, hiking, cooking, filmmaking, baking, magic-tricks
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, carrot, plum, peas, lime, grapes, radish
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 2. the person eating lime is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
 6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person eating cranberry##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
10. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Hobby           | filmmaking | cooking | woodworking | hiking | reading | baking | magic-tricks |
| Food   | cranberry    | lime   | peas      | grapes | plum    | carrot    | radish         |

