.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, action, epic, crime, western, musical
7 different games are played: go, backgammon, canasta, chess, mah-jongg, billiard, monopoly
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching epic movies##1
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 6. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
10. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre          | scientific | time-travel | crime | epic | western | musical | action |
| Game   | backgammon      | canasta   | chess   | mah-jongg      | go       | monopoly       | billiard     |

