.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: pink, apricot, ebony, green, fuchsia, aquamarine, white
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, december, january, october, september, march, november
 1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 4. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
12. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Color   | apricot | fuchsia     | ebony  | aquamarine       | pink       | white  | green   |
| Birthday    | march  | february | november | october | december | january | september |

