.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, milk, lemonade, 7up, juice, hot-chocolate
City: rome, london, edinburgh, marseilles, boston, venice, hannover
 1. the person drinking 7up is the person traveling to london##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 9. the person drinking milk is the person traveling to boston##1
10. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
11. the person traveling to hannover is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | juice    | hot-chocolate     | lemonade     | milk      | iced-tea | 7up      | fanta     |
| City   | marseilles | edinburgh | venice | boston | hannover | london | rome |

