.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, teacher, mechanic, paramedic, project-manager, engineer, lawyer
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: drama, satire, crime, horror, zombie, spy, thriller
 1. the teacher is the person watching thriller movies##1
