 3. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is the engineer##1
 6. the project-manager is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the mechanic is on the right of the teacher##1
 9. the paramedic is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the project-manager is on the right of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Job   | teacher | mechanic | engineer     | paramedic | lawyer | project-manager | architect |
| Movie-Genre     | thriller   | crime    | zombie | spy     | drama         | horror     | satire        |

