 3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing go##1
 4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
